    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;A Difficult Game About ROLLING&quot; - 是一个关于滚动的难题游戏。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/178d314d1e5ce793e1e237834b3c86b3.poster.avif?t=1750939474\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/178d314d1e5ce793e1e237834b3c86b3.webm?t=1750939474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/178d314d1e5ce793e1e237834b3c86b3.mp4?t=1750939474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>踏上一段无与伦比的旅程，通过崎岖的山脉、瀑布和古老的废墟，周围是无边无际的海洋，前往山顶。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/29417e22d6fcaf729e01da3c4f99468c.poster.avif?t=1750939474\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/29417e22d6fcaf729e01da3c4f99468c.webm?t=1750939474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/29417e22d6fcaf729e01da3c4f99468c.mp4?t=1750939474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你在一个球体里！你的身体为球的运动增加了一份混乱。爬到顶峰，旋转螺旋，并克服不可预测的物理路线。这一切都是你旅程的一部分。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/8878e99ddf0125e74d4c93fd19566b86.poster.avif?t=1750939474\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/8878e99ddf0125e74d4c93fd19566b86.webm?t=1750939474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/8878e99ddf0125e74d4c93fd19566b86.mp4?t=1750939474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>无情的物理：体验游戏独特的物理特性，球内的每一个重量和动量都给上升过程带来新的复杂性。您的每一个移动都需要仔细计算，每一个决定都必须权衡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/7bdb88d2034f698324798832000c9355.poster.avif?t=1750939474\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/7bdb88d2034f698324798832000c9355.webm?t=1750939474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901130/extras/7bdb88d2034f698324798832000c9355.mp4?t=1750939474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>坚持的哲学：这款游戏是对生活旅程的致敬，强调的哲学是路径，而不仅仅是到达顶峰，构成了真正的挑战。它是关于克服困难和在攀登中找到满足感。<br><br>难度与奖励：准备好迎接激烈的挑战。这款游戏旨在测试您的极限，但也会在您克服每一个障碍时，以深刻的满足感作为奖励。<br><br>高风险：每一个冒险的动作都带来回到起点的威胁。这款游戏尊重您的成就，但也惩罚鲁莽——小心行事，或者冒着失去一切的风险。<br><br>欢迎来到一个不仅挑战您的游戏技能，还挑战您的精神和决心的游戏。",
